<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 12:58:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>夜间潜行者 AH-6 小鸟直升机在伊朗前沿着陆点被摧毁</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/night-stalker-little-bird-helicopters-destroyed-at-forward-landing-site-in-iran</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在作为 F-15E WSO 救援中心的简陋机场的照片中，至少可以看到一架被烧毁的 AH/MH-6 小鸟。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/night-stalker-little-bird-helicopters-destroyed-at-forward-landing-site-in-iran"&gt;在伊朗前沿着陆点被摧毁的夜间追猎者 AH-6 小鸟直升机&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 10:11:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/night-stalker-little-bird-helicopters-destroyed-at-forward-landing-site-in-iran</guid></item><item><title>F-15E 武器系统官员在伊朗被击落已获救（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/f-15e-weapon-systems-officer-shot-down-over-iran-has-been-rescued</link><description>&lt;p&gt;据报道，经过大规模高风险搜索行动的激烈交火后，这名飞行员被美国特种作战部队救出。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/f-15e-weapon-systems-officer-shot-down-over-iran-has-been-rescued"&gt;F-15E 武器系统官员在伊朗被击落后已获救（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 10:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/f-15e-weapon-systems-officer-shot-down-over-iran-has-been-rescued</guid></item><item><title>伊朗通过高空集束弹头发射刺穿以色列的弹道导弹防御系统</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/iran-is-piercing-israels-ballistic-missile-defenses-with-high-altitude-cluster-warhead-releases</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在高空发射子弹药帮助伊朗突破了以色列的末段导弹防御系统，其他国家也可能会采取这种策略。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/iran-is-piercing-israels-ballistic-missile-defenses-with-high-altitude-cluster-warhead-releases"&gt;伊朗正在通过高空集束弹头释放刺穿以色列的弹道导弹防御系统，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 21:33:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/iran-is-piercing-israels-ballistic-missile-defenses-with-high-altitude-cluster-warhead-releases</guid></item><item><title>A-10 疣猪正在接受空中加油探测器测试</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthog-being-tested-with-aerial-refueling-probe</link><description>&lt;p&gt;除了 A-10 的胜利之外，在美国空军战术喷气机上安装加油探头可能是该军种敏捷作战部署战略的一大福音。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthog-being-tested-with-aerial-refueling-probe"&gt;正在接受空中加油探测器测试的 A-10 疣猪后&lt;/a&gt;模型首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;中。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 17:55:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthog-being-tested-with-aerial-refueling-probe</guid></item><item><title>F-15E 在伊朗坠落，救援行动正在进行（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/photos-of-f-15e-wreckage-emerge-amid-iranian-claims-it-shot-down-an-american-fighter</link><description>&lt;p&gt;F-15E 坠毁情况不明，美国战斗搜救装备已在伊朗深处被发现。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/photos-of-f-15e-wreckage-emerge-amid-iranian-claims-it-shot-down-an-american-fighter"&gt;F-15E 坠落伊朗后，救援行动正在进行（已更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 01:27:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/photos-of-f-15e-wreckage-emerge-amid-iranian-claims-it-shot-down-an-american-fighter</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-186</link><description>&lt;p&gt;再过两周……希望如此？&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-186"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 22:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-186</guid></item><item><title>SR-71 黑鸟船员拥有这些为他们定制的史密斯韦森手枪</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/sr-71-blackbird-crews-had-these-custom-smith-wesson-pistols-built-for-them</link><description>&lt;p&gt;早在 20 世纪 60 年代，空军就为 SR-71 黑鸟机组人员救生包订购了一小批特殊的 41 型手枪。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/sr-71-blackbird-crews-had-these-custom-smith-wesson-pistols-built-for-them"&gt;SR-71 后的黑鸟船员拥有这些为他们定制的史密斯韦森手枪，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;中。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 18:43:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/sr-71-blackbird-crews-had-these-custom-smith-wesson-pistols-built-for-them</guid></item><item><title>截至 2026 年 4 月 3 日的承运商追踪器</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/carrier-tracker-as-of-april-3-2026</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国第三艘航母打击群本周部署以支持史诗愤怒行动&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/carrier-tracker-as-of-april-3-2026"&gt;截至 2026 年 4 月 3 日的承运人追踪&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 18:16:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/carrier-tracker-as-of-april-3-2026</guid></item><item><title>因空袭而被切断的伊朗主要桥梁（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/key-iranian-bridge-severed-by-airstrikes</link><description>&lt;p&gt;德黑兰附近的这座桥梁是伊朗的重要动脉和骄傲的源泉，在特朗普威胁要轰炸该国“回到石器时代”后不久就被拆除。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/key-iranian-bridge-severed-by-airstrikes"&gt;伊朗关键桥梁被空袭切断的帖子（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 23:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/key-iranian-bridge-severed-by-airstrikes</guid></item><item><title>伊朗正在失去对伊拉克民兵的控制</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-is-losing-its-grip-on-iraqi-militias</link><description>&lt;p&gt;伊拉克的一名前一级运营商对伊朗支持的民兵针对美国利益的袭击激增提供了坦率的见解。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-is-losing-its-grip-on-iraqi-militias"&gt;伊朗正在失去对伊拉克民兵的控制&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 19:48:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-is-losing-its-grip-on-iraqi-militias</guid></item></channel></rss>